<lb n="0614a08"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0614a09"/>
<lb n="0614a10"/><head type="no">No. 1152</head>
<lb n="0614a11"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0614002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】麗本</note>佛說佛母般若波羅蜜多大明觀
<lb n="0614a12"/>想儀<note n="0614003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">軌＋（經）【明】＊</note><app n="0614003"><lem>軌</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">軌經</rdg></app></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0614a13"/>
<lb n="0614a14"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0614004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（宋）＋西【明】</note><app n="0614004"><lem>西</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">宋西</rdg></app>天<note n="0614005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔譯經〕－【明】</note><app n="0614005"><lem>譯經</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>三藏朝奉大夫試光祿卿
<lb n="0614a15"/>傳法大師<note n="0614006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔賜紫臣〕－【明】</note><app n="0614006"><lem>賜紫臣</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>施護奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0614a16"/><div1 type="jing"><p>爾時世尊。普為一切修出世間最上悉地者。
<lb n="0614a17"/>宣說佛母般若波羅蜜多大明觀想法</p>
<lb n="0614a18"/><p>彼大明曰</p>
<lb n="0614a19"/><p type="dharani">那謨<note place="inline">引</note>婆&CB00344;&CB00085;帝<note place="inline">引一<note n="0614007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔句〕－【明】</note><app n="0614007"><lem>句</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></note>阿哩也<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>倪
<lb n="0614a20"/>也<note place="inline">二合引</note>播<note place="inline">引</note>囉彌多<note place="inline">引</note>曳<note place="inline">引二</note>阿波哩彌多虞拏
<lb n="0614a21"/><note place="inline">引</note>曳<note place="inline">引三</note>薄訖底<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00085;蹉邏<note place="inline">引</note>曳<note place="inline">引四</note>薩哩&CB00085;<note place="inline">二
<lb n="0614a22"/>合</note>怛他<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00344;多倪也<note place="inline">二合引</note>那波哩布哩多<note place="inline">引</note>曳
<lb n="0614a23"/><note place="inline">引五</note>薩埵&CB00085;蹉邏<note place="inline">引</note>曳<note place="inline">引六</note>怛&CB00853;<note place="inline"><note n="0614008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">切身＝寧也切【明】</note><app n="0614008"><lem>切身</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">寧也切</rdg></app></note>他<note place="inline">引七</note>唵<note place="inline">引</note>
<lb n="0614a24"/>提<note place="inline">引八</note>率嚕<note place="inline">二合</note>底<note place="inline">九</note>娑蜜哩<note place="inline">三合</note>底<note place="inline">十</note>尾惹曳<note place="inline">引
<lb n="0614a25"/>十一</note>莎<note place="inline">引</note>賀<note place="inline">引十二</note></p>
<lb n="0614a26"/><p>如是大明有大功德。最上最勝不可思議。諸
<lb n="0614a27"/>修瑜伽行者。若欲觀想此大明字求悉地法。
<lb n="0614a28"/>先當發起大菩提心。然後依法於自心上想淨
<lb n="0614a29"/>月輪。於月輪中觀想提字。從臍輪轉於心而
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1152.0614b" n="0614b"/>
<lb n="0614b01"/>住。其字黃色是即般若波羅蜜多菩薩根本
<lb n="0614b02"/>心字。如是想已。復想此字即成般若波羅蜜
<lb n="0614b03"/>多菩薩。<note n="0614009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">想＝相【三】＊</note><note n="0614009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">想＝相【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0614009"><lem>想</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">相</rdg></app>此菩薩<app type="＊" source="0614009"><lem>想</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">相</rdg></app>身真金色有其六臂。
<lb n="0614b04"/>相好圓滿種種莊嚴頂戴寶冠。最上二手結
<lb n="0614b05"/>說法印。其印以二手作合掌。二中指入掌內
<lb n="0614b06"/>指面相合。二大指及二頭指。各各指面相捻。
<lb n="0614b07"/>餘指不動成印。餘手持般若波羅蜜多經。優
<lb n="0614b08"/>&CB00425;羅華。爍吉帝等。依法觀想如是想已。又復
<lb n="0614b09"/>諦想般若波羅蜜多大明。最上甚深從無我
<lb n="0614b10"/>生。由如是觀般若波羅蜜多無我生故。即一
<lb n="0614b11"/>切法無我平等。以如是平等故。即從般若波
<lb n="0614b12"/>羅蜜多。出生無邊諸文字相。文字相者攝一
<lb n="0614b13"/>切相諸修瑜伽行者若聞</p>
<lb n="0614b14"/><p type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E074;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>唵</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E1D5;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>提</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt>
<lb n="0614b15"/>　二字</p>
<lb n="0614b16"/><p>當於<note n="0614010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">頂＝項【三】</note><note n="0614010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">頂＝項【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0614010"><lem>頂</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">項</rdg></app>上而作觀想若聞</p>
<lb n="0614b17"/><p type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E074;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>唵</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A45E;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>詣</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt>
<lb n="0614b18"/>　二字</p>
<lb n="0614b19"/><p>當於舌端而作觀想若聞</p>
<lb n="0614b20"/><p type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E074;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>唵</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A4BC;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>&CB00768;</zi><sg type="fangie">仁齊切</sg></yin></t></tt>
<lb n="0614b21"/>　二字</p>
<lb n="0614b22"/><p>當於二耳輪而作觀想</p>
<lb n="0614b23"/><p>復次修瑜伽行者若欲觀想此佛母般若波羅
<lb n="0614b24"/>蜜多大明文字應當諦誠於自心上觀想八葉
<lb n="0614b25"/>大紅蓮華成曼拏羅於八葉位分布觀想大明
<lb n="0614b26"/>文字是諸文字各於方位不相間雜於蓮華東
<lb n="0614b27"/>葉位想安布</p>
<lb n="0614b28"/><p type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5A9;</t><t lang="chi">那</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5ED;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>謨</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt>
<lb n="0614b29"/>　二字</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1152.0614c" n="0614c"/>
<lb n="0614c01"/><p>於東南葉位想安布</p>
<lb n="0614c02"/><p type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5D9;</t><t lang="chi">婆</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A458;</t><t lang="chi">&CB00344;</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A656;</t><t lang="chi">&CB00085;</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A55D;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>帝</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt>
<lb n="0614c03"/>　四字</p>
<lb n="0614c04"/><p>於南葉位想安布</p>
<lb n="0614c05"/><p type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-CFC5;</t><t lang="chi">阿</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-DA47;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>哩也</zi><sg>二合</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-AABC;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>&CB00425;囉</zi><sg>二合</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E0A4;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>倪也</zi><sg>二合引</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5B5;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>播</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5FD;</t><t lang="chi">囉</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5E7;</t><t lang="chi">彌</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A557;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>多</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt>
<lb n="0614c06"/>
<lb n="0614c07"/><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5F7;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>曳</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt>
<lb n="0614c08"/>　九字</p>
<lb n="0614c09"/><p>於西南葉位想安布</p>
<lb n="0614c10"/><p type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-CFC5;</t><t lang="chi">阿</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5B5;</t><t lang="chi">波</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5FD;</t><t lang="chi">哩</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5E7;</t><t lang="chi">彌</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A557;</t><t lang="chi">多</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A45C;</t><t lang="chi">虞</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A54B;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>拏</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5F7;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>曳</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt>
<lb n="0614c11"/>　八字</p>
<lb n="0614c12"/><p>於西葉位想安布</p>
<lb n="0614c13"/><p type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5D9;</t><t lang="chi">薄</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E04D;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>訖底</zi><sg>二合</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A656;</t><t lang="chi">&CB00085;</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A67A;</t><t lang="chi">蹉</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A64B;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>邏</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5F7;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>曳</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt>
<lb n="0614c14"/>　六字</p>
<lb n="0614c15"/><p>於西北葉位想安布</p>
<lb n="0614c16"/><p type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A67A;</t><t lang="chi">薩</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-B7A3;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>哩&CB00085;</zi><sg>二合</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A557;</t><t lang="chi">怛</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A564;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>他</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A458;</t><t lang="chi">&CB00344;</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A558;</t><t lang="chi">多</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E0A4;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>倪也</zi><sg>二合引</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5A9;</t><t lang="chi">那</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5B5;</t><t lang="chi">波</t></tt>
<lb n="0614c17"/>
<lb n="0614c18"/><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A640;</t><t lang="chi">哩</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E042;</t><t lang="chi">布</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A640;</t><t lang="chi">哩</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A557;</t><t lang="chi">多</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5F7;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>曳</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt>
<lb n="0614c19"/>　十四字</p>
<lb n="0614c20"/><p>於北葉位想安布</p>
<lb n="0614c21"/><p type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A67A;</t><t lang="chi">薩</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A557;</t><t lang="chi">埵</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A656;</t><t lang="chi">&CB00085;</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A67A;</t><t lang="chi">蹉</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A64B;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>邏</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5F7;</t><t lang="chi">曳</t></tt>
<lb n="0614c22"/>　六字</p>
<lb n="0614c23"/><p>於東北葉位想安布</p>
<lb n="0614c24"/><p type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A557;</t><t lang="chi">怛</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A7EF;</t><t lang="chi">&CB00853;</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A564;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>他</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt>
<lb n="0614c25"/>　三字</p>
<lb n="0614c26"/><p>此八葉位次第想已於蓮華中心當想安布</p>
<lb n="0614c27"/><p type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E074;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>唵</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E1D5;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>提</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt>
<lb n="0614c28"/>二字</p>
<lb n="0614c29"/><p>復於蓮華內圍想分布八位於東位想</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1152.0615a" n="0615a"/>
<lb n="0615a01"/><p type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-AB61;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>率嚕</zi><sg>二合</sg></yin></t></tt>
<lb n="0615a02"/>一字</p>
<lb n="0615a03"/><p>東南位想</p>
<lb n="0615a04"/><p type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A4E8;</t><t lang="chi">底</t></tt>
<lb n="0615a05"/>一字</p>
<lb n="0615a06"/><p>南位想</p>
<lb n="0615a07"/><p type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-B2CE;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>娑蜜哩</zi><sg>三<note n="0615001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">合＋（一字）本文【三】</note><note n="0615001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">合＋（一字）本文【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0615001"><lem>合</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">合一字</rdg></app></sg></yin></t></tt></p>
<lb n="0615a08"/>
<lb n="0615a09"/><p>西南位想</p>
<lb n="0615a10"/><p type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A47E;</t><t lang="chi">底</t></tt>
<lb n="0615a11"/>一字</p>
<lb n="0615a12"/><p>西位想</p>
<lb n="0615a13"/><p type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A658;</t><t lang="chi">尾</t></tt>
<lb n="0615a14"/>一字</p>
<lb n="0615a15"/><p>西北位想</p>
<lb n="0615a16"/><p type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A4B6;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>惹</zi><sg type="fangie">仁左切</sg></yin></t></tt>
<lb n="0615a17"/>一字</p>
<lb n="0615a18"/><p>北位想</p>
<lb n="0615a19"/><p type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5F7;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>曳</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt>
<lb n="0615a20"/>一字</p>
<lb n="0615a21"/><p>東北位想</p>
<lb n="0615a22"/><p type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-DA49;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>莎</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A6A9;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>賀</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt>
<lb n="0615a23"/>二字</p>
<lb n="0615a24"/><p>如是觀想大明文字。各安布已。即當依法諦
<lb n="0615a25"/>想文字真理法門。或復依法憶念持誦。於日
<lb n="0615a26"/>三時依法布壇。<note n="0615002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">持＝特【宋】</note><app n="0615002"><lem>持</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">特</rdg></app>誦一百八遍。或一千八十
<lb n="0615a27"/>遍。若一月或六月。乃至一年不間斷者。即得
<lb n="0615a28"/>最上勝悉地法。又復若聞若持若誦者。是人
<lb n="0615a29"/>當得聞持具足證空三摩地。如是佛母般若
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1152.0615b" n="0615b"/>
<lb n="0615b01"/>波羅蜜多大明。最上甚深有大功德。修瑜伽
<lb n="0615b02"/>者<note n="0615003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">應＋（當）【三】</note><note n="0615003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">應＋（當）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0615003"><lem>應</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">應當</rdg></app>依法如是觀想</p>
<lb n="0615b03"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead>佛說佛母般若波羅蜜多大明觀想儀<app type="＊" source="0614003"><lem>軌</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">軌經</rdg></app></jhead></juan></div1>
</body></text></TEI.2>